text.tspan: Does the probability of a student buying from Pizza Hut increase when
There is no evidence from this small data set that the probability of
buying from Pizza Hut increases when the pizza price drops.
Students at Miami University were surveyed to evaluate how price affected whether
a pizza was ordered from Pizza Hut or another pizzeria. Of the students, 28 were
told the regular Pizza Hut price ($11.49) and 35 were given a reduced price ($8.49).
